  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We would like to collaborate and further develop an ipad-based, interactive quiz game
      'Emma'; to identify gaps in knowledge of inflammatory bowel disease in pediatric patients.
      These gaps can be used to improve patient education.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
