  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Improvement in patient knowledge of inflammatory bowel disease</measure>
    <time_frame>baseline to 18 months</time_frame>
    <description>The patient will play the ipad quiz game at office visits over time. We will look for improvements in overall knowledge of IBD, as well as subcategories (ex. nutrition, medications, etc.)</description>
