  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children 10-18 years of age

          -  Diagnosis of Crohn's disease or ulcerative colitis

          -  English-speaking

          -  Established patient of participating institution

        Exclusion criteria

          -  Inability to understand and read English at a grade 5-12 year level, as commensurate
             to their chronological age

          -  Research denial by patient or guardian
      </textblock>
